<$reveal state="$:/state/api-daiso-bma-1" type="match" text="yes" default="no" class="api-body" tag="div">

<p><strong>설명</strong><br>외부 API 혹은 기존 DB에서 ISBN으로 도서 정보를 사전 조회합니다.</p>

<p><strong>Parameters</strong></p>
<table>
<tr><th>Name</th><th>In</th><th>Type</th><th>Required</th></tr>
<tr><td>isbn</td><td>path</td><td>string</td><td>✓</td></tr>
</table>

<p><strong>Responses</strong></p>
<div class="api-resp-group">
<span class="api-resp resp-2xx">200</span> 조회 성공<br>
<span class="api-resp resp-4xx">400</span> ISBN 형식이 올바르지 않음<br>
<span class="api-resp resp-4xx">404</span> 해당 ISBN으로 검색된 도서 정보가 없음
</div>

<$reveal state="$:/state/schema-FindIsbnMetaData" type="match" text="yes" default="no" tag="div">
<$button class="api-schema-link" set="$:/state/schema-FindIsbnMetaData" setTo="no">→ FindIsbnMetaData ▾</$button>
</$reveal>
<$reveal state="$:/state/schema-FindIsbnMetaData" type="nomatch" text="yes" default="no" tag="div">
<$button class="api-schema-link" set="$:/state/schema-FindIsbnMetaData" setTo="yes">→ FindIsbnMetaData ▸</$button>
</$reveal>

<$reveal state="$:/state/schema-FindIsbnMetaData" type="match" text="yes" default="no" class="api-schema-body" tag="div">
<pre><code>{
  "refinedBook": {
    "isbn": "string",
    "title": "string",
    "index": "string",
    "description": "string",
    "authorList": ["AuthorInfoData"],
    "publisher": "string",
    "publicationDate": "string($date)",
    "price": "integer($int64)",
    "imageList": ["ImageRespDTO"],
    "volumeNo": "integer($int32)",
    "categories": ["CategoryRespDTO"],
    "tags": ["TagInfoData"]
  },
  "categoryList": {
    "categoryPathList": ["CategoryPath"]
  },
  "roleNameList": {
    "roleNames": ["string"]
  }
}</code></pre>
</$reveal>

</$reveal>
</div>

