<table>
<tr><th>Name</th><th>In</th><th>Type</th><th>Required</th><th>Description</th></tr>
<tr><td>pageable</td><td>query</td><td>unknown</td><td>✓</td><td>페이지 번호, 크기, 정렬 정보</td></tr>
<tr><td>X-User-Id</td><td>header</td><td>integer($int64)</td><td></td><td>사용자 식별 ID (선택 사항)</td></tr>
</table>

<p><strong>Responses</strong></p>
<div class="api-resp-group">
<span class="api-resp resp-2xx">200</span> 조회 성공
